@node "Main" "fd2StormC.rexx"
fd2StormC.rexx, Version 1.1

This little ARexx script saves you a lot of time.
It creates a pragma-file for the Storm-C/C++ Compiler from any given FD-file.
In this Version, ugly errors have now been fixed...

